         <head id="a3">COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
         <p>Correspondence about genealogical matters, undated notes and notebooks on genealogy of
            the Rice and related families, heraldry, genealogical methodology and bibliography;
            newspaper clippings, and eight pamphlets on genealogy and history.</p>
      </scopecontent>
